# DESIGN SPECIFICATION

The JSON above provides a complete specification for the mobile product details screen.  It leverages components from the design system where possible and falls back to native elements when necessary.  The three-container architecture is strictly adhered to, ensuring a robust and consistent mobile experience.  The design is optimized for mobile-first principles, user readability and interaction, and design system compliance. The "Product Details" title is concise and suitable for the app bar.  The complete product title is displayed as the first element in the content area, using the appropriate headline style.  Colors are referenced using their exact names and all components are fully specified.  The design incorporates a fallback mechanism for missing images and ratings. The structure is clean, easy to understand, and directly implementable by the engineering team.
